      <title>美国 PMI 未达标后新兴市场延续反弹至第二天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/emerging-market-stocks-sustain-recovery-as-mideast-concerns-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势有缓和的迹象，且美国经济数据疲软，引发人们对美联储可能采取不那么强硬立场的希望，新兴市场股市连续第二个交易日上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/emerging-market-stocks-sustain-recovery-as-mideast-concerns-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:47:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划再出售 12 亿美元但无法出售的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/trump-set-for-another-1-3-billion-in-shares-he-can-t-sell-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)的媒体初创公司上市的空白支票交易将在他实现目前从合并中获得的意外之财的某些目标后，再获得12亿美元的股票，但他仍然无法兑现其中任何一笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/trump-set-for-another-1-3-billion-in-shares-he-can-t-sell-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
